org.cougaar.core.blackboard
Class Subscription<E>

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.blackboard.Subscription<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CollectionSubscription, EnvelopeMetricsSubscription, PublisherSubscription, TimestampSubscription, TodoSubscription
public abstract class Subscription<E>
extends java.lang.Object

A filtered view of the blackboard that is updated between BlackboardService transactions.

The view is defined by the UnaryPredicate filter's "execute" method.

See Also:
CollectionSubscription, IncrementalSubscription

hasChanged

public final boolean hasChanged()
Check to see if this subscription has changed since the last transaction.

To be precise, this indicates if there were any visible changes to the subscription contents (add/change/remove) in the interval between the current and the previous calls to Subscriber.openTransaction()
